        <title>ACTIVITY: To calculate by selecting operations appropriate to solving problems [LO 1.8.8]</title>
        <para id="id1169085242618">1. Now that you know how to add and subtract decimal fractions, you can tackle the following activity. Work on your own. Calculate the following without using your pocket calculator:</para>
        <para id="id1169085242633">1.1 208,96 + 32,459 + 132,6</para>
        <para id="id1169085242649"/>
        <para id="id1169085242653"/>
        <para id="id1169085242658"/>
        <para id="id1169085242662"/>
        <para id="id1169085242666"/>
